e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8037f3327c5b7a14306b0a0961a0be31b31c6d1","tid":1528833,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"香港偉人"},{"pid":"2fb07f7032030d2c97f9d4f5ac07664919a28cdf","tid":1528833,"uid":175731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"林夕係大陸人唯一唔敢出聲屌既人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27cff4af691128828836c469113a9b87a4590d8","tid":1528833,"uid":172627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:30:33.000Z","msg":"當 習慣附和大家講的真理都得到獎賞<br />\n未慣十字路口挑選方向 離隊要膽量 拒絕跳牆<br />\n一輩子 血汗注入拍賣場 [誰被誰越抬越上]<br />\n一輩子 價值像泡沫上揚 誓與天較量<br />\n埋下理想栽種幻想"},{"pid":"3e8dd3f8c2d406f680cce2dae4df1996133687e7","tid":1528833,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"夢大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真香港人"},{"pid":"6ccb72ae58ae46364ad90d9b5a12dd4e45634e64","tid":1528833,"uid":295190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"好彩夕爺係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e818ba4fbcb7bed07b0278661729483c989e63c","tid":1528833,"uid":302704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"不槐為香港既夕爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkg